title: AP Sources: Seattle RB Jackson uninjured in car crash (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,415 AP Sources: Seattle RB Jackson uninjured in car crash (Yahoo Sports) Two people with knowledge of the situation say Seattle Seahawks running back Fred Jackson was uninjured when his car crashed outside the team's facility. Jackson was taken back to the team's facility and reported no injuries.
